> Upgrade your HelloFresh meal with this side bundle and serve sweet-and-savory glazed
> carrots as an added, quick side. We especially love these roasted carrots,
> tossed with Mike's Hot Honey & Garlic Herb Butter, alongside chicken, salmon,
> and pork chops, but they're delicious paired with any meal.

Adjust rack to top position and preheat oven to 425 degrees. Bring
@Garlic Herb Butter{1%ounce} to room temperature. Wash and dry produce.

Toss @Baby Carrots{1%pound} on a #baking sheet{} with a drizzle of
@Cooking Oil{1%teaspoon}, @Salt{}, and @Pepper{}.

Roast on top rack until tender and lightly browned, ~{18-22%minutes}.

Remove baking sheet from oven. Carefully toss carrots with softened
garlic herb butter and @Mike's Hot Honey®{2.25%ounce} to taste.